+ V_R0040_RESIDENT_GOVERNMENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_STAGE3_PROVISIONS;

    V_R0060_RESIDENT_GOVERNMENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0070_RESIDENT_GOVERNMENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0080_RESIDENT_GOVERNMENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +

WHERE REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE AND ROW_ID = 'R0030' AND COLUMN_ID ='C0040';

+ V_R0040_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3;


V_R0050_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 :=
    V_R0060_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0070_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0080_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0090_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0100_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0110_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0120_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0130_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0140_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0150_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0160_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0170_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0180_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0190_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0200_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0210_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0220_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0230_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0240_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0250_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0260_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3;


V_R0270_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 :=
    V_R0280_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0290_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0300_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0310_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0320_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +

+ V_R0040_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3;

    V_R0060_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0070_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0080_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0090_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0100_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +

    V_R0120_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +

    V_R0140_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0150_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0160_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0170_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0180_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0190_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0200_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0210_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0220_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0230_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0240_RESIDENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_LOANS_STAGE3 +

+ V_R0040_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;

    V_R0070_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +

    V_R0210_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0220_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +

    V_R0240_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0250_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0260_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;

    V_R0280_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0290_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0300_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0310_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0320_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0330_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +

    V_R0350_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;

    V_R0420_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0430_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0440_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0450_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0460_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;


V_R0470_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE :=
    V_R0480_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0490_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0500_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0510_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0520_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;


V_R0530_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE :=
    V_R0540_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0550_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0560_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0570_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0580_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0590_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0600_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0610_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0620_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0630_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0640_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0650_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0660_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0670_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0680_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0690_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0700_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0710_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;

V_R0720_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE :=
    V_R0730_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0740_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0750_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0760_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0770_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0780_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;


V_R0790_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE :=
    V_R0800_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0810_RESIDENT_SME_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;

-----R0030-C0170----

WHERE REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE AND ROW_ID = 'R0030' AND COLUMN_ID ='C0170';

+ V_R0040_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;


V_R0050_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE :=
    V_R0060_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0070_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0080_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0090_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0100_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0110_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0120_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0130_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0140_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0150_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0160_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0170_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0180_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0190_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0200_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0210_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0220_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0230_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0240_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0250_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0260_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;


V_R0270_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE :=
    V_R0280_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0290_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0300_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0310_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0320_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0330_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0340_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0350_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;

    V_R0450_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0460_RESIDENT_HNI_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;

-----R0030-C0210----

WHERE REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE AND ROW_ID = 'R0030' AND COLUMN_ID ='C0210';

+ V_R0040_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE;


V_R0050_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE :=
    V_R0060_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0070_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0080_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0090_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0100_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0110_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0120_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0130_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +
    V_R0140_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE +

+ V_R0040_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST;

    V_R0070_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0080_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +

    V_R0170_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0180_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0190_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0200_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0210_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0220_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0230_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0240_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0250_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0260_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST;

WHERE REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE AND ROW_ID = 'R0030' AND COLUMN_ID ='C0280';

+ V_R0040_RESIDENT_TRADEBILLS_LOANS_STAGE3;


V_R0050_RESIDENT_TRADEBILLS_LOANS_STAGE3 :=
    V_R0060_RESIDENT_TRADEBILLS_LOANS_STAGE3 +

-----R0030-C0330----
SELECT round(abs(nvl(sum(ACCT_BALANCE_IN_AED)/1000,0)))  INTO V_R0030_NON_RESIDENT_GOVERNMENT_PRIVATE_SECTOR_OUTSTANDING_BALANCE	FROM CBUAE_BRF5_5_DETAILTABLE 
WHERE REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE AND ROW_ID = 'R0030' AND COLUMN_ID ='C0330';

V_R0020_NON_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 :=  V_R0030_NON_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 
+ V_R0040_NON_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3;


V_R0050_NON_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 :=
    V_R0060_NON_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +
    V_R0070_NON_RESIDENT_GRE_LOANS_STAGE3 +

    V_R0620_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0630_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0640_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0650_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0660_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0670_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0680_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0690_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0700_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0710_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS;

V_R0720_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS :=
    V_R0730_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0740_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0750_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0760_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0770_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0780_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS;


V_R0790_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS :=
    V_R0800_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS +
    V_R0810_NON_RESIDENT_SME_STAGE3_PROVISIONS;

-----R0030-C0540----
SELECT round(abs(nvl(sum(ACCT_BALANCE_IN_AED)/1000,0)))  INTO V_R0030_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_LOANS_STAGE3	FROM CBUAE_BRF5_5_DETAILTABLE 
WHERE REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE AND ROW_ID = 'R0030' AND COLUMN_ID ='C0540';

-----R0040-C0540----

WHERE REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE AND ROW_ID = 'R0040' AND COLUMN_ID ='C0540';




-----R0060-C0540----

    V_R0690_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0700_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0710_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST;

V_R0720_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST :=
    V_R0730_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0740_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0750_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0760_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0770_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0780_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST;


V_R0790_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST :=
    V_R0800_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST +
    V_R0810_NON_RESIDENT_INDIVIDUALS_PROVISION_INTEREST_LEGACY_INTEREST;
